(1, 1, 'learn-php-tutorial', 'Learn PHP', '		  		  		  		  		  		  <h1>PHP tutorial</h1><p>PHP is the abbreviation of the English hypertext preprocessor language Hypertext Preprocessor. PHP is an HTML embedded language, a scripting language for embedding HTML documents that is executed on the server side.</p><p>PHP is a powerful server-side scripting language for creating dynamic interactive sites.</p><p>PHP is free and widely used. At the same time, for competitors like Microsoft ASP, PHP is definitely another efficient option.</p><h2>Learn PHP by example</h2><p>Our PHP online example allows you to learn PHP more easily, including PHP source code and running results.</p>\n<textarea class=\"code\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt; \n&lt;html&gt;\n&lt;body&gt; \n&lt;?php\necho \"Hello PHP!\"; \n?&gt; \n&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;\n</textarea> \n		   \n		  ', 'learn php,learning php,how to learn php,learn php fast,	learn php online,php machine learning,learn php free', 'Learn PHP Step by Step | jQuerylearn.com', 'PHP is a powerful server-side scripting language for creating dynamic interactive sites. Especially suitable for web development and can be embedded in HTML. Its syntax takes advantage of C, Java, and Perl and is easy to learn.', '2018-07-06 12:32:44', 'akshay'),
(2, 1, 'php-tutorial', 'PHP tutorial', '		  		  <h1>PHP tutorial</h1><p>This PHP tutorial will give you deep knowledge about PHP (hypertext pre-processing).In this tutorial we will teach you how to use PHP in easy way .This PHP tutorial will cover all the Topics such as Introduction,Array,Functions,date and time, regular expression, PHP Maths, PHP Loops and Use of Mysql .</p><h2>What Is PHP Actually ?</h2><p></p><ul><li>PHP means(Hypertext Preprocessor)</li><li>PHP is Server side Programming Language</li><li>PHP is faster than other scripting languages</li></ul><p></p>\n\n<b>One Example:</b><div><div style=\"background: #f0f3f3; overflow:auto;width:auto;border:solid gray;border-width:.1em .1em .1em .8em;padding:.2em .6em;\"><pre style=\"margin: 0; line-height: 125%\"><span style=\"color: #009999\">&lt;?php\necho</span> <span style=\"color: #CC3300\">\"MY NAME IS AKSHAY\"</span>;  \n<span style=\"color: #009999\">?&gt;</span>  \n</pre></div>\n\n\n\n<b><div><b><br></b></div>Output:</b><div><div class=\"codeblock3\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(213, 221, 198);width: 100%;margin: 8px 0px 0px;background: rgb(249, 251, 249);padding: 0px 0px 0px 5px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">MY NAME IS AKSHAY</span></div></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>This tutorial is so easy right :)</div> \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		  </div> \n		   \n		  ', 'php tutorial,php tutorials,php tutorial point,php mysql tutorial,php tutorial for beginners,php class tutorial,mysql php tutorial', 'PHP tutorial (Hypertext Preprocessor)  ', 'This PHP tutorial will give you deep knowledge about PHP (hypertext pre-processing).In this tutorial we will teach you how to use PHP in easy way .This PHP tutorial will cover all the Topics such as Introduction,Array,Functions,date and time, regular expression, PHP Maths, PHP Loops and Use of Mysql .', '2018-07-06 12:32:44', 'akshay'),
(3, 1, 'what-is-php', 'What is PHP', '		  <h1>What is php ?</h1><div>PHP is popular server side scripting language used to create web application .Using this language you can create dynamic pages . According to developers ,this is fastest language to develop an application.</div><div><br></div><div>Php is really easy language to lean . If you know how to play with HTML,CSS,JQUERY , it will be very easy for you to learn PHP .I learn PHP with in 3 months .This website<a href=\"http://jquerylean.com\"> jquerylean.com</a> is also created using PHP language.</div><h1>About PHP</h1><div><ul><li>PHP is open source language</li><li>PHP is Interpreted Language(No need Compilation)</li><li>PHP is OOPS Based</li><li>PHP is easiest Language to learn</li><li>PHP full form is Hypertext Preprocesing</li></ul><div><br></div></div><div><br></div> \n		   \n<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ScMrdoxH16U\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\n		   \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		  ', 'what is php,what does php stand for,what is php used for', 'What is php ?', 'PHP is easiest server language available on internet .You can create your first website with in 3 months gangrened.Go for this tutorial series and lea', '2018-07-06 12:32:44', 'akshay'),
(4, 1, 'Installation-of-php', 'Installation of PHP', '		  <h1>Installation of PHP</h1><p>PHP is a development language. The code written in the development language usually needs to run under the specified software. Therefore, the code we write needs to be displayed (running), and we need to install these software to run the code.</p><p>We can refer to the development of several software running our code and software running the code.</p><h1>What do you need to do ?</h1><p>As a beginner, we don\'t recommend downloading Apache MySQL PHP and configuring it yourself, because in the configuration, you will encounter a lot of problems, which will weaken your confidence in the beginning. So I suggest you use the integrated environment package at the beginning.</p><p>Third, choose the integrated environment package</p><p>There are a lot of integrated environment packages available for you to choose from, and the functions are similar. You can choose one. Commonly there are  <b>WAMPServer, XAMPP, APMserv, AppServer.</b></p><p>  </p><div><b>If you have trouble in installation .Please watch this video :</b></div><div><b><br></b></div><div><b><br></b></div>\n\n<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kVc_9vAO7oI\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe> \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		   \n		  ', 'install php,install php on windows,install php windows,install php ubuntu', 'Installation of PHP on local server for your first page .', 'PHP is a development language. The code written in the development language usually needs to run under the specified software. Therefore, the code we write needs to be displayed (running), and we need to install these software to run the code.', '2018-07-06 12:32:44', 'akshay'),
