amily: monospace; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(242, 253, 255);\">3 1</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(242, 253, 255);\">3 2</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(242, 253, 255);\">3 3</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(242, 253, 255);\">3 4</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(242, 253, 255);\">4 1</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(242, 253, 255);\">4 2</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(242, 253, 255);\">4 3</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(242, 253, 255);\">4 4</span></div></div>&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Thats it . :)&nbsp;</div><div><b><br>Like use on top right :)</b></div><div><br></div><div><br></div></div>', 'php, tutorial, example, file, session, date, array, functions, time, xml, ajax, mysql, mysql, regex, string, oop', 'PHP For Loop - jQuerylearn', 'PHP For Loop with examples and practical experiments , php file, php session, php date, php array, php form, functions, time, xml, ajax, php mysql, regex, string, oop', '2018-07-06 12:32:44', 'akshay'),
(18, 2, 'php-get-and-post', 'PHP learn - While Loop', '<h1>PHP learn While Loop</h1><div>This is simplest way to apply the loop .&nbsp;loops of code until the condition become true.<b> See the example :</b></div><div><br></div>\n\n<!-- HTML generated using hilite.me --><div style=\"background: #f0f3f3; overflow:auto;width:auto;border:solid gray;border-width:.1em .1em .1em .8em;padding:.2em .6em;\"><pre style=\"margin: 0; line-height: 125%\"><span style=\"color: #009999\"><!--?php</span-->&lt; ?php\n<span style=\"color: #006699; font-weight: bold\">while</span> (expr)<span style=\"color: #555555\">:</span>\n    statement\n    <span style=\"color: #555555\">...</span>\n<span style=\"color: #006699; font-weight: bold\">endwhile</span>;\n\n<span style=\"color: #009999\">?&gt;</span>\n</span></pre></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Example below define value <b>$j</b> = 1. The loop will repeat until the<b> value of $j</b> is equal to 3 or less than 3.</div><div><br></div><!-- HTML generated using hilite.me --><div style=\"background: #f0f3f3; overflow:auto;width:auto;border:solid gray;border-width:.1em .1em .1em .8em;padding:.2em .6em;\"><pre style=\"margin: 0; line-height: 125%\"><span style=\"color: #009999\">&lt; ?php <!--?php</span-->\n<span style=\"color: #003333\">$i</span> <span style=\"color: #555555\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #FF6600\">1</span>;\n<span style=\"color: #006699; font-weight: bold\">while</span>(<span style=\"color: #003333\">$i</span> <span style=\"color: #555555\">&lt;=</span> <span style=\"color: #FF6600\">3</span>){\n    <span style=\"color: #003333\">$i</span><span style=\"color: #555555\">++</span>;\n    <span style=\"color: #006699; font-weight: bold\">echo</span> <span style=\"color: #CC3300\">\"The number is \"</span> <span style=\"color: #555555\">.</span> <span style=\"color: #003333\">$i</span> <span style=\"color: #555555\">.</span> <span style=\"color: #CC3300\">\"<br>\"</span>;\n}\n<span style=\"color: #009999\">?&gt;</span>\n</span></pre></div><b><div><b><br></b></div><div><b><br></b></div><div><b><br></b></div><div><img title=\"php while loop\" alt=\"php-while-loop\" src=\"https://jquerylearn.com/uploads/photo_15317497471.jpeg\"></div><div><b><br></b></div>&nbsp; &nbsp;</b><div><b>See the video Example below to know More :</b><br><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hO0YOOeJrOE\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\n\n</div> \n		  ', 'PHP While Loop,php, tutorial, example, file, session, date, array, functions, time, xml, ajax, mysql, mysql, regex, string, oop', 'PHP learn - While Loop | jQuerylearn', 'PHP While Loop with examples and practical experiments , php file, php session, php date, php array, php form, functions, time, xml, ajax, php mysql, regex, string, oop', '2018-07-06 12:32:44', 'akshay'),
(19, 2, 'php-do-while-loop', 'PHP learn -  Do While Loop', '<h1>PHP learn -&nbsp; Do While Loop</h1><div><p>The difference between do...while and while is that their values ​​are checked at different timings.<br></p><p>Do-while Regardless of whether the while judgment is true, the code code block loop statement is executed once and guaranteed to be executed once (the true value of the expression is checked after each loop).<br>However, our while loop above will check the Boolean decision area and set it up. If it is not established, it will not be executed.</p><p></p></div><div><b>Example :</b><!-- HTML generated using hilite.me --><div style=\"background: #f0f3f3; overflow:auto;width:auto;border:solid gray;border-width:.1em .1em .1em .8em;padding:.2em .6em;\"><pre style=\"margin: 0; line-height: 125%\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 153, 153);\">&lt;?php</span>\n<span style=\"color: #006699; font-weight: bold\">Do</span>{\n\n<span style=\"color: #0099FF; font-style: italic\">//executed code;</span>\n\n}<span style=\"color: #006699; font-weight: bold\">while</span> ( condition is <span style=\"color: #006699; font-weight: bold\">true</span> );\n\n<span style=\"color: #009999\">?&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>&nbsp;<div>The following example first sets the variable <b>$x to 1 ($x=1)</b>. Then, the do while loop outputs a string and increments the variable<b> $x by 1</b>. Then check the conditions<div><p></p><p>Check (<b>$x</b> is less than or equal to <b>5</b>). As long as $x is less than or equal to<b> 5</b>, the loop will continue to run, anyway, the loop ends</p> <b>Example :</b> </div></div><!-- HTML generated using hilite.me --><div style=\"background: #f0f3f3; overflow:auto;width:auto;border:solid gray;border-width:.1em .1em .1em .8em;padding:.2em .6em;\"><pre style=\"margin: 0; line-height: 125%\"><span style=\"color: #009999\"> &lt;?php</span>\n Header(<span style=\"color: #CC3300\">\"Content-type:text/html;charset=utf-8\"</span>); <span style=\"color: #0099FF; font-style: italic\">//Set the encoding</span>\n <span style=\"color: #003333\">$x</span><span style=\"color: #555555\">=</span><span style=\"color: #FF6600\">1</span>;\n <span style=\"color: #006699; font-weight: bold\">Do</span> {\n     <span style=\"color: #006699; font-weight: bold\">Echo</span> <span style=\"color: #CC3300\">\"This number is: </span><span style=\"color: #AA0000\">$x</span><span style=\"color: #CC3300\"> &lt;br&gt;\"</span>;\n     <span style=\"color: #003333\">$x</span><span style=\"color: #555555\">++</span>;\n } <span style=\"color: #006699; font-weight: bold\">while</span> (<span style=\"color: #003333\">$x</span><span style=\"color: #555555\">&lt;=</span><span style=\"color: #FF6600\">5</span>);\n <span style=\"color: #009999\">?&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>&nbsp;<div><b>Output:</b></div><div><b><br></b></div><div><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">This number is 1</font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">This&nbsp;number is 2</font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">This&nbsp;number is 3&nbsp;</font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">This&nbsp;number is 4&nbsp;</font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">This&nbsp;number is 5</font></div><div><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br></font></div><div><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><div>Try this program on your computer .</div><div><br></div></font></div>\n\n', 'Do While Loop,learn php,php, tutorial, example, file, session, date, array, functions, time, xml, ajax, mysql, mysql, regex, string, oop', 'PHP learn -  Do While Loop jQuerylearn', 'PHP Do While Loop with examples and practical experiments , php file, php session, php date, php array, php form, functions', '2018-07-06 12:32:44', 'akshay'),
