(40, 6, 'php-mysql-select', 'MYSQLi SELECT', '		  		  		  <h1>MYSQLi SELECT</h1><div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Read data from a MySQL database</span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">We learned to add data to the database. In this section, how do we read the data from the database and display it on the page?</span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Query data with select</span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></div><table class=\"table table-bordered\"><tbody><tr><td><b>Category<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; white-space: pre;\">	</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">    </span></b></td><td><b>Detailed explanation</b></td></tr><tr><td>Basic grammar</td><td>Select * from table;</td></tr><tr><td>Instance<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; white-space: pre;\">	</span></td><td>Select * from MyGuests;</td></tr><tr><td> Example description</td><td>Query all results in all fields in the MyGuests table</td></tr></tbody></table><div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Note <b>: \" * \"</b> is a regular expression that means matching all</span></div><div> </div><div><b><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Instance</span>\n</b><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\"></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">We query the data we added to the MyGuests table and display it on the page.</span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><!--?php</span--></span></div><pre><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Header(\"Content-type:text/html;charset=utf-8\"); //Set the encoding<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> $servername = \"localhost\";<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> $username = \"root\";<br>