uttons, check boxes, or buttons</font></font></td></tr></tbody></table><table width=\"-642\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(237, 241, 242);\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><tr class=\"firstRow\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><td width=\"193\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;details&gt;</td><td width=\"193\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Used to describe the details of a document or part of a document</font></font></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><td width=\"193\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;dialog&gt;</td><td width=\"193\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Define dialogs, such as prompt boxes</font></font></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><td width=\"193\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;summary&gt;</td><td width=\"193\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The label contains the title of the details element</font></font></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><td width=\"193\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;figure&gt;</td><td width=\"193\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Specify separate stream content (images, charts, photos, code, etc.).</font></font></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><td width=\"193\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;figcaption&gt;</td><td width=\"193\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Define the title of the &lt;figure&gt; element</font></font></td></tr></tbody></table><table width=\"-642\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(237, 241, 242);\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><tr class=\"firstRow\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><td width=\"193\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all;