(88, 8, 'html5-new-element', 'HTML5 new elements', '		  		  		   <h1>HTML5 new element</h1><div><br></div><div>HTML 4.01 has changed a lot since 1999. Today, several of the HTML 4.01 have been deprecated and these elements have been removed or redefined in HTML5.</div><div><br></div><div>In order to better handle today\'s Internet applications, HTML5 adds a lot of new elements and features, such as: graphics rendering, multimedia content, better page structure, better form processing, and several api drag and drop elements, positioning, Includes web application caching, storage, web workers, and more.</div><div><b><br></b><h2>&lt;canvas&gt; new element&nbsp;</h2></div><table width=\"-642\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(20, 25, 30); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(237, 241, 242);\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><tr class=\"firstRow\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><td width=\"193\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">label</strong></span></td><td width=\"193\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;description</strong></span></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><td width=\"193\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 5px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0